研究是否跟隨歐盟和內地做法，停止輸入巴西急凍肉類，稍後會有詳細公布。<br />\n<br />\n凍肉海產批發及零售商會前秘書長表示，市面上的凍肉有三成至三成五來自巴西，主要是較為廉價的肉類產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=214879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214879&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=aa5e4310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214879&h=e48aa34c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=214879</a></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n中國雞有事唔見政府即刻停止輸入</blockquote><br />\n福喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港柒咪係照食"},{"pid":"1770e9c8c7d9c671ff14832d16a1bc9a9277fec9","tid":165226,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>消息：政府正研究停止輸入巴西急凍肉<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府正研究是否停止輸入巴西急凍肉類。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，食物安全中心正研究是否跟隨歐盟和內地做法，停止輸入巴西急凍肉類，稍後會有詳細公布。<br />\n<br />\n凍肉海產批發及零售商會前秘書長表示，市面上的凍肉有三成至三成五來自巴西，主要是較為廉價的肉類產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=214879\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214879&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=aa5e4310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214879&h=e48aa34c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=214879</a></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n中國雞有事唔見政府即刻停止輸入</blockquote><br />\n福喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港柒咪係照食</blockquote><br />\n重有藉口停巴西美國野<br />\n咁大陸野就做可以再壯大市場之餘再鍊住你春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4513d471ff125921a00db8a8b5c7cedfa6e1c18","tid":165226,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa